net.rom.utility.system.property

Class SunSystemProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.rom.utility.system.property.SunSystemProperties

  • public final class SunSystemProperties
extends Object
    Contains SystemProperty fields that represent all known Sun system properties. These properties comprise the majority of properties whose keys begin with "sun.".
